> Top News No. 7 LSU too much for displaced South Carolina, 45-24 Fans watch from the stands during the second half of an NCAA college football game between LSU and South Carolina in Baton Rouge, La., Saturday, Oct. 10, 2015. LSU won 45-24. The game was moved from Columbia, S.C. to Baton Rouge because of flooding. (AP Photo/Jonathan Bachman) The most compelling, sharable stories from across the web.
